Name: Rapid Fire
About the game: Rapid Fire is an arcade shooter game based on virtual reality. Become a gunman in the west, avoid bullets coming from all directions, avoid civilians who run away from the villains through precise aiming, and eliminate the villains. Shoot with a revolver, shoot with a shotgun, sweep enemies with a machine gun and prove your skills on the leaderboard
